CHANGE 12 — Split requirements.txt into prod and dev
- Keep requirements.txt for production dependencies only 
  (remove pytest, httpx).
- Create requirements-dev.txt with: pytest, httpx, and any other test-only packages.
- Update CONTRIBUTING.md setup instructions to reference requirements-dev.txt.

